{
  "stem": "7598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he rented a large home in Lapan, and his parents, my mother's parents, his brother who, with whom he was associated in business, who was a partner in his business and my mother's youngest brother's wife and two children were with us.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The brother was in the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We all went to Lapan where, I suppose, we just waited for the events to happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was about an hour and a half away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was between Ostend and the Belgian-- and the French border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the idea was to get as near to the French border as possible in case things would happen and we would want to get to France.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I suppose one felt that the French army certainly would be very strong and that if one ever did get to France, one would be safe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went by, by car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We hired cars, and we went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father didn't have a car before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in Lapan for very few days because we heard that the Panzer divisions were approaching very fast and, in fact, we were already surrounded by the Germans, but we weren't aware of this.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was asked that before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I, I didn't feel badly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know whether I didn't feel badly because later on worse things happened or whether I took it as an adventure.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I honestly can't answer that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But were all at the seaside, I suppose, with the hope of going back to our home, you know, when the war is over or when the fighting is over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But within a very short while, you know, we realized that things weren't that easy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think then we all became very, very frightened.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
